WEBVTT

00:09.084 --> 00:10.752
Ba-bum.

00:17.062 --> 00:20.251
<i>Previously on</i>
"The Dragon Prince"...

00:20.512 --> 00:21.885
It's up to us now.

00:21.980 --> 00:23.853
We have to return this egg.

00:23.932 --> 00:27.159
We have to keep it safe
and carry it to Xadia.

00:27.227 --> 00:28.628
And find its mother.

00:30.605 --> 00:32.457
Aunt Amaya?

00:36.778 --> 00:38.509
I'm so glad you're safe.

00:38.947 --> 00:41.034
Though it is a heavy burden,

00:41.121 --> 00:45.408
I will humbly take up the battle
in Harrow's name.

00:45.495 --> 00:47.310
Stop the coronation!

00:47.377 --> 00:49.724
The princes are alive!

00:50.917 --> 00:52.207
What now?

00:52.294 --> 00:54.401
Ugh. I don't think a boat...

00:54.469 --> 00:55.509
Just get in.

